title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Infiltrate Fort Zancudo in The Brute Force File
content:
Set your sights on the hangar below Fort Zancudo in The Brute Force File — where you’ll suit up and sneak into the notorious military base, then make a break for it behind the controls of a Scarab tank.

The weekly Priority File offers an increased GTA$ payout, and all FIB Files from GTA Online: Agents of Sabotage feature optional mission challenges that award bonus GTA$ and Career Progress rewards.
